===Etymology===
{{blend|spam|indexing}}

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun-unc}}

#{{internet}} The practice of deliberately and dishonestly manipulating [[search engine]]s either to increase the likelihood of a [[website]] or [[page]] from a website being listed near the beginning of the results returned by the search engine or to influence the category to which the page is assigned.

